## Abstract:
##   Configuration file ~/.unburden-home-dir.list instructs the unburden-home-dir utility what files and directories to
## unburden the home directory from.
##
## Details:
##   None.
##
## References:
## - Unburden Your Home Directory
##   --> https://github.com/xtaran/unburden-home-dir#readme
